"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 03, 2025</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104vuv1665702701508.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/vuv1665702701508.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/vuv1665702701508.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"vuv1665702701508\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Key </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"vuv1665702701508__key_311235\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">A Key is a Development Object that designates a field or combination of fields as a\n      Primary Key, Candidate Key, or Index. </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vuv1665702701508__p_d95090e1_d95091e1_d95092e1\">A Database Entity or a Modeled Entity that is in\n         relationship with another entity must have a primary key, and may have one or more\n         candidate keys and indexes.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vuv1665702701508__topic_d63377e1_d63378e1_d63379e1_d63380e1_d63381e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d548760e56\"> Characteristics </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"vuv1665702701508__table_d10523e1_d10524e1_d10525e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vuv1665702701508__table_d10523e1_d10524e1_d10525e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Characteristics</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vuv1665702701508__table_d10523e1_d10524e1_d10525e1__entry__2\"></th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vuv1665702701508__table_d10523e1_d10524e1_d10525e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Icon:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vuv1665702701508__table_d10523e1_d10524e1_d10525e1__entry__2\">\n<div class=\"p\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"vuv1665702701508__fig_w25ab1b5b5b3b3b7b1b3b1b1_w26ab1b5b5b3b3b7b1b3b1_w27ab1b5b5b3b3b7b1b3_w28ab1b5b5b3b3b7b1_w29ab1b5b5b3b3b7_w30ab1b5b5b3b3_w31ab1b5b5b3_w32ab1b5b5_w33ab1b5_w34ab1\">\n<img alt=\"Icon\" class=\"image\" id=\"vuv1665702701508__image_prx_mml_mwb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/key.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vuv1665702701508__table_d10523e1_d10524e1_d10525e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Object type code:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vuv1665702701508__table_d10523e1_d10524e1_d10525e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">key</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vuv1665702701508__table_d10523e1_d10524e1_d10525e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Main Development Object?</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vuv1665702701508__table_d10523e1_d10524e1_d10525e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">No</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vuv1665702701508__table_d10523e1_d10524e1_d10525e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Part of:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vuv1665702701508__table_d10523e1_d10524e1_d10525e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"tza1665702561698.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tza1665702561698.html\" title=\"A Modeled Entity is an Entity that defines a logical data aggregation at an abstract level. It is used to model the default properties and code of an entity, so that the Entity can be referenced and inherited by derived entities in components.\">Modeled Entity</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vuv1665702701508__table_d10523e1_d10524e1_d10525e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Contains:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vuv1665702701508__table_d10523e1_d10524e1_d10525e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jgi1665702550212.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jgi1665702550212.html\" title=\"A Property is a named, typed attribute of Development Object that defines a characteristic or behavior of the object. Each property has a descriptive name, a literal name, a data type, and a value. If no value is specified, a default value may be used.\">Property</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vuv1665702701508__table_d10523e1_d10524e1_d10525e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Generalization:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vuv1665702701508__table_d10523e1_d10524e1_d10525e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ulo1665702550460.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ulo1665702550460.html\" title=\"A Uniface Development Object is an abstract data type that defines the characteristics and behavior of a logical application unit, such as a Component, Field, Message, Library, and so on.\">Development Object</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vuv1665702701508__table_d10523e1_d10524e1_d10525e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Specializations</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vuv1665702701508__table_d10523e1_d10524e1_d10525e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fhj1665702701588.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fhj1665702701588.html\" title=\"A Primary Key is a Key that uniquely identifies an occurrence of an Entity. Every database entity requires a primary key, which is used to ensure that occurrences are unique in a database table and to define relationships between modeled entities.\">Primary Key</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yjw1665702701673.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yjw1665702701673.html\" title=\"A Candidate Key is an optional Key that uniquely identifies an occurrence of a Database Entity. An entity can have multiple candidate keys each defining a unique combination of fields that uniquely identify an occurrence.\">Candidate Key</a>,\n                              <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gym1665702564527.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gym1665702564527.html\" title=\"Get or set the index (position) of a node in a Struct collection.\">$index</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vuv1665702701508__table_d10523e1_d10524e1_d10525e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Compilation Output:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vuv1665702701508__table_d10523e1_d10524e1_d10525e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vuv1665702701508__table_d10523e1_d10524e1_d10525e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">URI format:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vuv1665702701508__table_d10523e1_d10524e1_d10525e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">ent:<var class=\"keyword varname\">ModeledEntityName</var>/key:<var class=\"keyword varname\">KeyName</var>\n</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vuv1665702701508__topic_d63382e1_d63383e1_d63384e1_d63385e1_d63386e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d548760e288\"> Specialization </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vuv1665702701508__p_d95099e1_d95100e1_d95101e1\">Key specializes Development Object in the following\n            ways:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vuv1665702701508__li_d37442e1_d37443e1_d37444e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vuv1665702701508__p_d95102e1_d95103e1_d95104e1\">It has a Modeled Entity as parent.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vuv1665702701508__li_d37445e1_d37446e1_d37447e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vuv1665702701508__p_d95105e1_d95106e1_d95107e1\">It has no child objects.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vuv1665702701508__li_d37448e1_d37449e1_d37450e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vuv1665702701508__p_d95108e1_d95109e1_d95110e1\">It has a <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Type</span> property\n                  that specifies whether it is a primary, candidate, or index key.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vuv1665702701508__topic_d63387e1_d63388e1_d63389e1_d63390e1_d63391e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d548760e321\"> Properties </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vuv1665702701508__p_d95114e1_d95115e1_d95116e1\">Object Properties:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vuv1665702701508__li_d37451e1_d37452e1_d37453e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jrq1665702585385.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jrq1665702585385.html\" title=\"Name of the development object, which uniquely identifies it.\">Name</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vuv1665702701508__li_d37454e1_d37455e1_d37456e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"owq1665702585461.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/owq1665702585461.html\" title=\"Type of Development Object. Read only.\">Type</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vuv1665702701508__li_d37457e1_d37458e1_d37459e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ybn1665702585544.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ybn1665702585544.html\" title=\"Complete URI of the Development Object. Read only.\">Location</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vuv1665702701508__li_d37460e1_d37461e1_d37462e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xrw1665702585620.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xrw1665702585620.html\" title=\"Use this property to briefly describe the development object in up to 256 Unicode characters.\">Description</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vuv1665702701508__li_d37463e1_d37464e1_d37465e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ipc1665702585697.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ipc1665702585697.html\" title=\"Use this property to provide comments or instructions for the selected development object. You can use the toolbar and standard Windows keyboard shortcuts to format the text, copy and paste, and undo and redo edits.\">Documentation</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vuv1665702701508__p_d95117e1_d95118e1_d95119e1\">Configuration Properties:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vuv1665702701508__li_d37466e1_d37467e1_d37468e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gxv1665702701743.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gxv1665702701743.html\" title=\"Ordered list of fields comprising the specified Key of a Modeled Entity.\">Key Fields</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vuv1665702701508__p_d95120e1_d95121e1_d95122e1\">Behavior Properties:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vuv1665702701508__li_d37469e1_d37470e1_d37471e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ivd1665702701816.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ivd1665702701816.html\" title=\"Determines whether the fields that make up the key are validated automatically. Valid values are T (default) or F.\">Validate</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vuv1665702701508__li_d37472e1_d37473e1_d37474e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zak1665702701886.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zak1665702701886.html\" title=\"Type of key. Valid types are Primary, Candidate, or Index.\">Key Type</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ruk1704361429324.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Keys</a><p>A key is a field or combination of fields that uniquely identifies occurrences of entities.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3616616\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3616616\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Key Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 03, 2025 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Key A Key is a Development Object that designates a field or combination of fields as a Primary Key, Candidate Key, or Index. A Database Entity or a Modeled Entity that is in relationship with another entity must have a primary key, and may have one or more candidate keys and indexes. Characteristics Characteristics Icon: Object type code: key Main Development Object? No Part of: Modeled Entity Contains: Property Generalization: Development Object Specializations Primary Key , Candidate Key , $index Compilation Output: — URI format: ent: ModeledEntityName /key: KeyName Specialization Key specializes Development Object in the following ways: It has a Modeled Entity as parent. It has no child objects. It has a Type property that specifies whether it is a primary, candidate, or index key. Properties Object Properties: Name Type Location Description Documentation Configuration Properties: Key Fields Behavior Properties: Validate Key Type Related Links Keys A key is a field or combination of fields that uniquely identifies occurrences of entities. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}